+
+## Scope
+
+Plan only for R2 storage configuration standardization.
+
+Approved standard:
+
+- Configuration variable: `GAMEFOUNDRY_STORAGE_PROJECTS_PREFIX`
+- Allowed project storage prefixes:
+  - `/dev/projects/`
+  - `/ist/projects/`
+  - `/uat/projects/`
+  - `/prod/projects/`
+
+Allowed APPLY/build scope:
